name: fnlSlider
tagline: Simple horizontal slider plugin for jQuery
body:
fnlslider
=========

Simple horizontal slider plugin for jQuery. Call the jQuery plugin with a data array and a template callback function, and you are set to go.

See /src for source, demo/ for a demo.
I've commented the extension and the demo extensively.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
